boolean: (Regsvr32 OR (regsvr32 AND /I OR /s OR http IR https OR ftp OR scrobj.dll))
label: commandline

boolean: ((nc  OR netcat) AND ( -z OR -w OR -nlvp OR -nv OR -n OR -l OR -v OR -p OR -e))
label: tool

boolean: ((post OR curl OR wget OR get) AND (.js OR .zip OR .php OR .aspx OR exe OR .xml OR .txt))
label: web

boolean: (lhost OR rhost OR lport OR rport)
label: tool

boolean: (mshta AND (javascript OR .hta OR vbs OR http OR https OR winword OR excel OR powerpnt OR cmd OR powershell OR wscript OR cscript OR sh.exe OR bash.exe OR reg OR bitsadmin))

boolean: (kernel32.dll OR msvcrt.dll) AND (memset OR virtualalloc OR createthread))
label: script

boolean: (netsh AND advfirewall AND (action AND allow) OR show)
label: enumeration

boolean: (netsh AND (portproxy OR listenport OR listenaddress OR connectport OR connectaddress))
label: tool

boolean: (ms-settings AND Shell AND Open AND command)
label: commandline
